        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "去愁容忍悲泪问娘金安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尚香见驾，母后千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇儿平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐座。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢母后。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？我儿今日进宫身穿素服，面带泪痕是何缘故？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母后哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时才宫人报道，刘皇叔晏驾白帝城了……"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！刘皇叔晏驾白帝城了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！可伤啊可伤呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为此，女儿身穿孝服，要到江边一祭；特来辞别母后。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴国太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去往江边祭奠，多有不便；不如就在宫中备下祭礼，祭奠一番也就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，母后哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙尚香",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "母后说话理太偏，"
